    "Question": {
      "content": "Which of these is not part of the layers of triploblastic organisms?",
      "options": [
        "Mesoderm",
        "Ectoderm",
        "mesogloea",
        "Endoderm"
      ],
      "type": "OBJ"
    },
    "Answer": {
      "type": "string",
      "content": "mesogloea"
    },
    "Explanation": {
      "type": "string",
      "content": "Triploblastic animals have three germ layers (ectoderm, mesoderm, endoderm); mesogloea is a gelatinous layer in diploblastic organisms like jellyfish."
